<p>When trying to understand the various ways Real Madrid played during the LaLiga season, it’s important to look at goals such as; Goals For (GF) and Goals against (GA) utilizing these two different data, gives a chance to understand the strength the team has when tackling with goals and also help’s to evaluate the team’s perfomance and strength when it comes to scoring and the tatics that lead to this point.</p>
<p>I used Football Ref to get better insights about the goals across the season, creating a line chart has helped me evaluate the team strength better and understand what season did they do better in goal’s.</p>
<p>Studying a chart about the Goals, gives more information about the teams defesne, pace and tatics when it comes to balls.</p>
